1<p<\infty 
L_{V}^{p}(-1,1)=\left \{ f:(-1,1)\rightarrow \mathbb{R}:\int_{-1}^{1}\left | f(x) \right |^{p}V(x)dx<\infty  \right \}
\left \| f \right \|_{L_{V}^{p}}=(\int_{-1}^{1}\left | f(x) \right |^{p}V(x)dx)^{\frac{1}{p}}
W\subset L_{V}^{p}(-1,1)
